						<summary>

						<p>Hero-stone kept in the Siddharāmēśvara temple outside the village.</p>						

						<p>Mallidēva 13th century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This short inscription is dated Vikrama, Chaitra ba. 1, Sunday. The date is irregular.</p>						

						<p>It registers the death in a fight of Bēyi-Nāyaka who bore the epithet <hi rend="italic">kāḍānemalla</hi> (wrestler with wild elephant) among others.</p>						

						</summary>
